Package seng202.group7.analyses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comparer
    This class adds a set of static methods that allow reports to distance and time to be compared.
    CrimeFrequency
    A class that holds a String date and int frequency, a list of crime frequency is used for crime over graphing
    GraphUtil
    A set of static utility methods that prepares material for the graph view classes, such as ranking data based on frequency or preparing strings to be displayed as a graph title.
    Tuple<X,​Y>
    Tuple class used for converting hash table into sorted list for the "GraphUtil" data class.
